ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Export Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the EXPORT CONTROL LIST in order to make various changes, including the amendment to the definition of the term “guide”, updates to the various commitments made in the multilateral export control and non-proliferation regimes in which Canada participates, as well as a minor editorial modification identified by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
